   (b) Distribute MNEMOS as part of Licensee's commercial offering
   (c) Create derivative works of MNEMOS for commercial purposes
   (d) Host MNEMOS on Licensee's infrastructure for fee-paying customers

   COMMERCIAL USE RIGHTS

   This license permits the following:

   ✓ Operating MNEMOS as a SaaS or cloud memory service
   ✓ White-labeling MNEMOS memory infrastructure in your product
   ✓ Reselling MNEMOS to third parties
   ✓ Creating proprietary derivative works based on MNEMOS
   ✓ Bundling MNEMOS with other commercial products
   ✓ Charging customers for access to MNEMOS-backed features
   ✓ Multi-tenant hosting with per-customer namespace isolation
   ✓ Federated memory networks offered as a managed service
   ✓ Commercial support and SLA agreements
   ✓ Custom integrations and enterprise deployments

   RESTRICTIONS

   This license does NOT permit:

   ✗ Open-sourcing proprietary modifications under incompatible terms
     (proprietary modifications stay proprietary)
   ✗ GPL or other copyleft relicensing of the Work
   ✗ Sublicensing to third parties without explicit written approval
   ✗ Transferring the license without written consent
   ✗ Removing or obscuring copyright and attribution notices

   PAYMENT TERMS

   Commercial licensing fees are based on:
   - Annual subscription for commercial use
   - Seats / monthly active users (if applicable)
   - Revenue share model (optional)
   - Enterprise support tiers

   Specific pricing available upon request.

   TERM AND TERMINATION

   - Initial term: 12 months from purchase
   - Renewal: Annual renewal required (pricing may change)
   - Termination: Either party may terminate with 30 days written notice
   - Effect of termination: Licensee must cease all commercial use within 30
     days of termination

   SUPPORT AND MAINTENANCE

   Commercial licensees receive:
   - Priority bug fix support
   - Quarterly security updates
   - Documentation and API access
   - Optional: Custom development and integration services

